    "has_raw_measurements": true,
    "raw_measurement_details": "The paper reports raw experimental measurements of electrical resistivity, Hall resistivity, specific heat, torque magnetometry, and magnetization on single crystals of Ce3Bi4Pd3, Ce3Bi4Pt3, and La3Bi4Pd3. Measurements were performed in DC fields up to 37 T at HFML-EMFL, pulsed fields up to 65 T at NHMFL-LANL, and low-temperature setups in Vienna including a PPMS with 3He option and an Oxford dilution refrigerator. The paper does not specify file formats for the raw data.",
